<section class="grids-section" id="five-grids">
<div class="section-inner">
<div class="section-eyebrow">In detail</div>
<h2 style="margin-bottom:8px;">The five grids.</h2>
<p class="lead-text" style="margin-bottom:36px;">Every role is read across five dimensions. Together they build a fuller, fairer picture of role size than title or job description alone.</p>
<div class="grid-cards">
<div class="grid-card js-grid" onclick="toggleGridCard(this)"><div class="grid-card-top"><span class="grid-card-num">01</span><span class="grid-card-badge skills">Skills required</span></div><h3>Technical skills</h3><p>Knowledge level and how that knowledge is applied in practice.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card js-grid" onclick="toggleGridCard(this)"><div class="grid-card-top"><span class="grid-card-num">02</span><span class="grid-card-badge skills">Skills required</span></div><h3>Managerial skills</h3><p>Coordination of work and business decision-making authority.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card js-grid" onclick="toggleGridCard(this)"><div class="grid-card-top"><span class="grid-card-num">03</span><span class="grid-card-badge skills">Skills required</span></div><h3>Persuasive skills</h3><p>The extent to which the role must influence others to create value.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card js-grid" onclick="toggleGridCard(this)"><div class="grid-card-top"><span class="grid-card-num">04</span><span class="grid-card-badge context">Organisational context</span></div><h3>Control</h3><p>The scale of operational responsibility attached to the role.</p></div>
<div class="grid-card js-grid" onclick="toggleGridCard(this)"><div class="grid-card-top"><span class="grid-card-num">05</span><span class="grid-card-badge context">Organisational context</span></div><h3>Impact</h3><p>How significant the role is within the organisation.</p></div>
</div>
<p class="stepper-more">Each grid is explained dimension by dimension, with worked examples, in the <a href="/guides/methodology-guide/">Methodology Guide</a>.</p>
</div>
